{"tid":346854,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(痴撚線影展)警世爛片《台北物語》獲選香港坎坷影展開幕電影","createTime":"2017-08-04T09:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T16:03:33.000Z","uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d690f043bf831467d48304449b5e931ed880d93e","tid":346854,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"Festival de Cannot 坎坷影展<br />\n<br />\n昨天 19:20<br />\n<br />\n［香港觀眾有眼福］隆重宣佈坎坷影展開幕電影&mdash;&mdash;《台北物語》（香港首映）！2017年最強坎坷電影，以低成本創造票房奇蹟，堪稱台灣low bud版天機，其偏鋒美學震撼華語電影界！<br />\n<br />\n#坎坷影展<br />\n#開幕電影<br />\n#台灣強片引入<br />\n#日期地點稍後公佈<br />\n#售票詳情嗰啲都係啦"},{"pid":"558634075c75af1e18943efd9de72dbb71f38d93","tid":346854,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ba68f970a6d0bc4068f1674fc0fd92aabb36ffd","tid":346854,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0cfda9c9d4d6eab12c080340e11499bb499690","tid":346854,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"Festival de Cannot 坎坷影展<br />\n8月6日 18:57 &middot; <br />\n［陀地強片］隆重宣佈坎坷影展閉幕電影《香港大師》（宇宙首映）！由《關公大戰外星人》導演梁仲文執導、恐懼鳥編劇，用最復古嘅未來感講述2047年古惑仔的江湖恩怨。本地超隱世電影類型科幻中長片破天荒登上大銀幕！導演梁仲文將出席「閉幕電影暨坎坷影展頒獎禮」見證坎坷一刻！<br />\nG.V.A. Creative 梁仲文化 恐懼鳥 Scary Bird<br />\n預告片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pICbbdgrvDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpICbbdgrvDI&d=YuSwjyxktyc1RY4LuWNYjP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ff264e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pICbbdgrvDI</a><br />\n#坎坷影展<br />\n#坎坷閉幕<br />\n#未開始賣飛<br />\n#所以一票難求<br />\n#最坎坷票務安排<br />\n#時間地點遲些再說<br />\n#比古惑仔更中二病喔<br />\n#科幻古惑仔堪稱MK之霸<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20664628_338002833293762_1960933515180758623_n.jpg?oh=c1b955d1eeae4fce3762b4c06d47e5d8&amp;oe=59F2C93B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20664628_338002833293762_1960933515180758623_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dc1b955d1eeae4fce3762b4c06d47e5d8%26oe%3D59F2C93B&h=3d282b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKung Fury咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cfecd06ab6c65cb5050e8366129ba5d1162be5","tid":346854,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"呢個坎坷影展啲選片好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669cdf796e757bd3589385d03b1b3807ccd08ba6","tid":346854,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個坎坷影展啲選片好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無完整選片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb6ab884a0e3cf878593cf94cc4eae3dfda96f8","tid":346854,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個坎坷影展啲選片好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無完整選片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暫時公佈左呢兩套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nfb page <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Festival-de-Cannot-%E5%9D%8E%E5%9D%B7%E5%BD%B1%E5%B1%95-301348613625851/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%